<div class="container-fluid ">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class='mb-4' data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Who we are</h1>
        <h3 class="mb-0" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">The Konnex Resources team is focused on working
            with regulators, consultants, and the people of Central Idaho to responsibly advance the Empire Mine
            Project.</h3>
        <p class="text-lg mt-60 py-70 text-darkblue" width="100%" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">
            Konnex is based in Mackay, Idaho, and is a U.S. operating company of Phoenix Copper Limited. The Konnex team
            shares Phoenix Copper’s commitments to environmental stewardship, social responsibility, and economic
            sustainability. We take great pride in the opportunity to work with all stakeholders to bring the area’s
            rich legacy of mining into the future.
        </p>
        <a class="red-btn mt-5" asp-page="/KonnexResources" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Learn More</a>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="container services py-80 pb-100">
