</div>
<div class="col-md-12 pb-100">
    <h1 class="mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">What we do</h1>
    <h3 data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Empire Mine Project </h3>
    <p class="text-lg py-4 pl-70 text-darkblue" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Konnex Resources is focused
        on bringing Mackay, Idaho’s proud history of copper, zinc, gold, and silver mining into the future. The
        underground Empire Mine near Mackay was in operation from 1901 to 1942 and helped support a strong economy in
        the town. The Konnex team is proposing to generate similar economic benefits in the area by developing Empire
        into an open pit mine which will providing high-paying jobs to area workers and require the purchase of supplies
        and services from local businesses. Technological advances and environmental protection laws enable our team to
        develop a sustainable project that can help meeting the growing needs of green energy.
    </p>
    <a class="blank-red-btn" asp-page="/Project" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Learn More</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="metals-bg">
    <div class="metals-box">
        <h1 data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Why it matters</h1>
        <h3 data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">More than Minerals</h3>
        <p class="text-lg py-4 pl-70" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Copper and other metals are central to
            the world’s transition to a clean energy future. Governments around the world are taking action to move away
            from fossil fuels and accelerate the use of renewable energy technologies. Responsible mining companies like
            Konnex Resources are working to help meet the growing demand with operations that are sustainable for both
            the environment and local communities.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg py-4 pl-70" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Konnex Resources is committed to being
            a leader in the industry when it comes to environmental standards, social responsibility, and transparent
            governance (ESG). The goals of the Company’s ESG committee are to identify and implement ways the Company
            can exceed the environmental standards required by law, facilitate opportunities for local residents to have
            their interests represented, encourage transparency between Konnex and surrounding communities, and more.
        </p>
        <a class="blank-red-btn text-white" asp-page="/ESG" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Learn More</a>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid py-100 pr team-container mt-60">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row flex-center calc-left">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <img class="img-fluid w-100" src="images/group-img.jpg" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5 px-50">
                <h1 class="text-white" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Get Involved</h1>
                <h3 class="text-white" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Join the Konnex Community
                    Advisory Team!</h3>
                <p class="text-white text-md mt-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">The mission of KCAT is to
                    create an enduring model of partnership, transparency, and accountability between Konnex and the
                    local communities. Anyone living within Custer and Butte Counties is welcome to apply for KCAT’s
                    next open position.</p>
                <a class="red-btn mt-md-4 mb-3" href="#" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

